gantt
    title Project Schedule
    dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat %m-%d

    section Design
    Requirements       :done, requirements, 2026-01-05, 5d
    Architecture       :done, architecture, after requirements, 4d

    section Delivery
    Implementation     :active, implementation, after architecture, 10d
    Integration test   :integration, after implementation, 5d
    Release            :milestone, release, after integration, 0d
